claim.claim-text:
1. A breast-bounce inhibitor comprising: 
a bounce-prevention strap articulated for suspension laterally over tops of a woman's breasts; 
a first back-strap attachment on a first end of the bounce-prevention strap; 
a second back-strap attachment on a second end of the bounce-prevention strap; and 
the bounce-prevention strap having bounce-resistant resilience intermediate the first back-strap attachment and the second back-strap attachment.

13. A breast-bounce inhibitor comprising: 
a bounce-prevention strap articulated for suspension laterally over tops of a woman's breasts; 
a first back-strap attachment on a first end of the bounce-prevention strap; 
a second back-strap attachment on a second end of the bounce-prevention strap; 
the first back-strap attachment is a bra-strap extension from a first side of a bra back strap of a bra; 
the second back-strap attachment is a bra-strap extension from a second side of the bra back strap of the bra; and 
the bounce-prevention strap having bounce-resistant resilience intermediate the first back-strap attachment and the second back-strap attachment.
